race.comment: The penny has dropped for former NSW galloper MIND OVER MATTER (3) who has put back-to-back wins together here with Cormack being in the irons on both occasions. Looks ready to for the step-up in trip now and can easily bring up the hat-trick without surprising. VALUBIOUS (11) is one from one over this track and trip and will be rock-hard fit for this. Only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a major role in the outcome. Former Victorian OH SO THRILLING (2) is having her first run for the new stable but should find this easier than what she faced down south. Respect any market confidence. SILVER CITY (4) is a four-time winner over this distance range and can feature from the favourable draw. WINNING SAGA (8) rounds out the selections in a race with only a handful of chances.
